{"tid":446288,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[釣厹]駱克道邂逅靚女到沙灘短聚 男子一覺醒來財物盡失","createTime":"2017-10-24T07:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T09:02:53.000Z","uid":120541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0e2b27661db13a5fb6bde5c7d38dab58cfbcd4","tid":446288,"uid":120541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T07:16:11.000Z","msg":"駱克道邂逅靚女到沙灘短聚 男子一覺醒來財物盡失 <br />\n<br />\n新增影片<br />\n港島深水灣泳灘，早上7時許，一名<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">姓葉男子(48歲)</span>致電報警稱，凌晨3時許，在灣仔駱克道一帶，邂逅一名中國籍女子，雙方談得投契，結伴乘的士到深水灣泳灘，坐在沙灘望着繁星吹着海風，繼續飲酒談心。惟至清晨一覺醒來，卻發現自己孤身一人，女伴已經不知所終，身上一條價值7萬元的金鏈、3,000元港幣及3,000元人民幣不翼而飛，懷疑是該女子偷去。由於他自覺酒量不差，懷疑有人在酒中落藥將他迷暈，以致不省人事，瞓到天光。<br />\n<br />\n救護員到場將男事主送院檢驗，只見他沒有受傷，但腳步不穩，稍後由警員扶助，到警署作進一步調查。警方經初步調查，將案列作盜竊，交由西區警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171024/57369499\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171024%2F57369499&d=TeY7SAw3qJ28urUpDWKnMGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=65344db6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171024%2F57369499&h=d4a3e4d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171024/57369499</a><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/24/151159_ac721462f0d4a163d1edd66c6bf1f1dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F24%2F151159_ac721462f0d4a163d1edd66c6bf1f1dc.jpg&h=cd4de605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n笑撚到hihi<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/24/151610_c9974583f1a965b642ee997a8877d230.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F24%2F151610_c9974583f1a965b642ee997a8877d230.jpg&h=ea9045f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"559ebb4881c4641e7671198761006e60cfbae1ef","tid":446288,"uid":38047,"like":0,"dislik